      <div id="LCPDelta-content">
        <h3><a href="https://lcpdelta.com/">LCP Delta</a></h3>
        <em>Analyst, Connected Home Service and Energy Insights+ Service (June 2022 - Present)</em>
        <p><em>Edinburgh, Scotland</em></p>
        <ul>
          <li>Planned and wrote reports to achieve a monthly deliverable for the connected home and energy insights+ subscription services.</li>
          <li>Conducted research calls with key industry players to understand the market size and strategic challenges of energy suppliers, HVACs, and controls companies.</li>
          <li>Carried out desk-based research on the market landscape for customer engagement platforms, electric heating systems and controls.</li>
          <li>Managed competing obligations of deliverables across two research services as well as consultancy projects as and when required.</li>
        </ul>
