      <img src="images/clearwater-analytics-logo.png" alt="Clearwater Analytics Logo" id="clearwater-logo">
      <div id="clearwater-content">
        <h3><a href="https://clearwateranalytics.com/">Clearwater Analytics</a></h3>
        <em>Implementation Analyst, Global Delivery (June 2021 - May 2022)</em>
        <p><em>Edinburgh, Scotland</em></p>
        <ul>
        <li>Led calls with insurance and asset management clients to ensure smooth and successful transition from their legacy system onto the Clearwater platform.</li>
        <li>Reconciled clients’ accounts ensuring multiple asset classes (derivatives, bonds and equities) were accurately modelled; discrepancies were investigated to either be fixed or provide an explanation that the client was satisfied with and signed-off.</li>
        <li>Collaborated with multiple departments through Jira to ensure clients’ holdings and general ledger entries were accurate on the Clearwater platform. This is based on accounting standards in addition to custodian, asset manager, and third party data.</li>
        <li>Achieved an award for execution for “delivering against yearly targets and closing out projects no matter the expectations or challenges faced”.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      

      <img src="images/cnooc-logo.png" alt="CNOOC International Logo" id="cnooc-logo">
      <div id="cnooc-content">
        <h3><a href="https://cnoocinternational.com/">CNOOC International</a></h3>
        <em>MEng Industrial Placement, Plant Optimisation Team (June - December 2019)</em>
        <p><em>Aberdeen, Scotland</em></p>
        <ul>
          <li>Investigated the value-add of installing multiphase flow meters on the Buzzard Oil Field in the North Sea.</li>
          <li>Forecasted potential losses due to well testing and estimated the cost of installation of multiphase flow meters. Installation had potential value of up to <strong>£7 million</strong>.</li>
          <li>Wrote an industry quality report for CNOOC on the benefits, both quantitative and qualitative, of installing multiphase flow meters. This report graded First-Class.</li>
          <li>Recommended the most suitable multiphase flow meter supplier for CNOOC’s requirements.</li>
          <li>Updated, and produced new, process flow diagrams and piping & instrumentation diagrams.</li>
          <li>Collected data through face-to-face meetings, telephone calls and emails from a wide range of internal business sections, external vendors and external contractors.</li>
          <li>Completed BOSIET and MIST offshore training prior to going offshore to the Buzzard platform to liaise with the offshore workers.</li>
          <li>Developed a Gantt chart project plan, aided by mentor, alongside weekly project updates that led to successful on-time completion of the project.</li>
          <li>Planned and coordinated a Hazard and Operability Study to identify the potential risks of installing multiphase flow meters and mitigate them.</li>
          <li>Documented process calculations to be easily accessible and auditable.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      

